org.primaresearch.dla.page

Class Page.MeasurementUnit

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.primaresearch.dla.page.Page.MeasurementUnit
  • Enclosing class:
    Page

    public static class Page.MeasurementUnit
extends java.lang.Object
    Measurement unit for coordinates.
    Introduced to support ALTO XML files. Use XmlInputOutput.postProcessPage(...) to scale all coordinates using the image information.
